<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="L" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Left" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Left,</orth> on the side opposed to the right: <bibl n="shak. ven 158" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 158</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tgv 2.3.16" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. II, 3, 16</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 3.2.148" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. III, 2, 148</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 4.3.25" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL IV, 3, 25</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 5.303" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. V, 303</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 2.2.44" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 2, 44</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 5.177.44" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 177</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. shr 4.1.95" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. IV, 1, 95</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 4.5.102" default="NO" valid="yes">All's IV, 5, 102</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 3.1.43" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C III, 1, 43</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 2.1.163" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. II, 1, 163</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jc 1.3.16" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. I, 3, 16</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jc 5.1.17" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 17</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 2.3.119" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. II, 3, 119</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 2.2.37" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. II, 2, 37</bibl>. <cit><quote>leaving the fear of God on the l. hand,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.2.24" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. II, 2, 24</bibl></cit>, i. e. disregarding it.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>